{"type": "article", "id": 10393, "title": "针孔照相机", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-04T07:30:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235552bkXgLOn71xQcJaEo.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\tONDU 一直致力于针孔照相机的设计和制作，最近他们推出了一系列针孔照相机。相机所有的木制材均取自当地森林里面的胡桃木和枫木，表面涂有设计师自己制作的蜂蜡和天然油脂的混合物，用作一个保护层。此外，相机使用磁铁作为连接固定。目前，他们正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，如果对针孔照相机感兴趣，不妨<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ondu-/ondu-pinhole-cameras-mk-ii/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-family:Helvetica;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235548KLJZYBkfDa5V1N4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235548RC7me0JpHtQVoqdG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235549Q4cjSwMl7B8FkHEx.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235549Za8tQ74kqBIicgAo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235550EO1kK78rIsVwTeft.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235550dJ2uMNUcxqH05V9l.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235551CaO84gHRpV3WXIL7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.34107579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}